<bibRefCitation id="2A904DEBCDEA6171B778ADE454804067" author="Shatrovskiy, OG." journalOrPublisher="The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette" pageId="0" pageNumber="423" refId="B13" refString="Shatrovskiy, OG., Kravchenko, OM, 2016. To the study the beetles of the families Helophoridae, Hydrochidae, Spercheidae, Hydrophilidae, Hydraenidae, Elmidae, Dryopidae and Heteroceridae (Coleoptera) of the Shatsky National Natural Park. The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette 24(1): 45-61. [in Ukrainian]." title="To the study the beetles of the families Helophoridae, Hydrochidae, Spercheidae, Hydrophilidae, Hydraenidae, Elmidae, Dryopidae and Heteroceridae (Coleoptera) of the Shatsky National Natural Park. The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette 24 (1): 45 - 61. [in Ukrainian]." year="2016">Shatrovskiy and Kravchenko 2016</bibRefCitation>
