<bibRefCitation id="AD8F8D0D0AD7D8D3C42B634756C265C0" author="Shatrovskiy, AG" journalOrPublisher="The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette" pageId="0" pageNumber="423" pagination="5 - 10" refId="B12" refString="Shatrovskiy, AG, 2017. New data on the distribution of Palearctic species of water scavenger beetles from the nominative subgenus of the genus Berosus Leach, 1817 (Coleoptera: Hydrophilidae). The Kharkov Entomological Society Gazette 35 (2): 5 - 10" title="New data on the distribution of Palearctic species of water scavenger beetles from the nominative subgenus of the genus Berosus Leach, 1817 (Coleoptera: Hydrophilidae)." volume="35" year="2017">Shatrovskiy 2017</bibRefCitation>
